Call TEXTE(22321,TIT) From OBJDIV
Return

$SETCLE
Local Char CLEPRIM(GLONAVA) , CLESEC(GLONAVA)(0..0) , CLELIG(GLONAVA)
CLEPRIM = 'COD'
Return

$OPTIONS
